Joshua Harris (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joshua_Harris_(actor) 0 Joshua Harris (born November 27, 1978) is an American former child actor, former baseball player, and television producer. He is known for playing Christopher Ewing on the primetime soap opera Dallas from 1985 to 1991.
